<cc:SdkSinglePageViewer
  Name    ="_e707ec59_8b22_473e_b77c_3060a237517a"
  Tag     ="Make a TextBox Control Read-Only"
  xmlns:cc="clr-namespace:Microsoft.Windows.SdkViewer.Controls;assembly=SdkViewer"
  xmlns   ="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation">
  <FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation">
    <Table CellSpacing="5">
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph FontSize="22"><Run>How to: Make a TextBox Control Read-Only</Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

        <TableRow/>
      </TableRowGroup>

    </Table>

    <Paragraph>This example shows how to configure a TextBox control to not allow user input or modification. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph FontSize="22">Example
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>To prevent users from modifying the contents of a <Run FontWeight="Bold">TextBox</Run>
 control, set the IsReadOnly attribute to <Run FontWeight="Bold">true</Run>
.
    </Paragraph>

    <Table CellSpacing="5">
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph FontSize="22"><Run>XAML </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph xml:space="preserve" TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="8pt" FontFamily="Courier New"><Run>
&lt;TextBox IsReadOnly="True" > The user may not modify the contents of this TextBox. 
&lt;/TextBox> </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

      </TableRowGroup>

    </Table>

    <Paragraph>The <Run FontWeight="Bold">IsReadOnly</Run>
 attribute affects user input only; 
it does not affect text set in the Extensible Application Markup Language (XAML) description of a <Run FontWeight="Bold">TextBox</Run>
 control, or text set programmatically through the Text property. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>The default value of <Run FontWeight="Bold">IsReadOnly</Run>
 is <Run FontWeight="Bold">false</Run>
.
    </Paragraph>

